Welcome to Thesaurus!
(Kurna palq Thesaurus)

Thesauri are a very polite people and will always say hello and bye.

Thesauri love to eat cheese, fish and pork.

Their kids also like candy but you have to get it under the counter.
In Thesauri, 'no' is just like 'yes', only written backwards.

Thesauri numbers only go up to five.

They don't have the concept of zero.

Qacli plaw Thesaurus!

The Thesauri people love fish, cheese and meat. Their kids also like candy but you have to specifically ask for it at a store.

In Thesauri, the opposites (white and black, hot and cold) are written backward.
